race.comment: GOLD MINER (4) is a promising dog in the frame at three of 10 starts including five wins and was in the minors again latest (19.81) over 340m at this track. Tends to go well on this box draw. Happy to have her on top this line-up. STAR SIRIUS (1) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 4.5 lengths into second (19.77) at this track in a Mix 2/3 over 340m. Will give a great sight again. EXEMPLARY (2) is in hot form after clocking a handy 22.24 victory two back then followed up with a 29.76 win at The Gardens over 515m last time. In form and looks a leading player again. BEAR MAN (7) among the chances again based on last run here.

runners.name: Nicmac Star
